id - Variable in class LMS.entities.Delivery
Unique id of this delivery.
InterationalDelivery - Class in LMS.entities
An international delivery within the Logistics Management System.

For international deliveries a factor can be set that is used to calculate customs when crossing borders.

This factor is applied to the goods' total value when calculating the total of an international delivery.

InterationalDelivery(long, String, String) - Constructor for class LMS.entities.InterationalDelivery
Constructs an international delivery with specified id, pickup and drop off location.

The id must be greater than 0.
InterationalDelivery(long, String, String, float) - Constructor for class LMS.entities.InterationalDelivery
Constructs an international delivery with specified id,custom factor, pickup and drop off location.

The id must be greater than 0 and the custom factor must be greater than or equal to 1.

If the id is invalid an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.
isAssigned() - Method in class LMS.entities.Delivery
Status indicating whether a carrier has been assigned to this delivery.
isCollected() - Method in class LMS.entities.Delivery
Status indicating whether the goods of this delivery have been handed to the delivery service provider.
isDelivered() - Method in class LMS.entities.Delivery
Status indicating whether the goods of this delivery have been delivered to the destination by the delivery service provider.
Item - Class in LMS.entities
A shipping item within the Logistics Management System.

A shipping item consists one or many identical single items with a common description a single item mass and value.
Item(String, int, float, long) - Constructor for class LMS.entities.Item
Constructs a shipping item with specified description, amount, single item mass and single item value.
All numerical values must be greater than zero.
